## PlainText.cleanupRemovedNodes() method

`cleanupRemovedNodes` cleans up nodes that have been removed. The cleaned nodes are subject to garbage collector collection.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
cleanupRemovedNodes(ticket: TimeTicket): number;
```
